<section class="relative grid min-h-screen place-content-center overflow-hidden pt-20">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-carbon mb-4 leading-tight">
        ¿Quieres probar algo distinto sin arriesgarte?<br />
        <span class="text-plum-soft">No te preocupes.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-carbon/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Descubre postres y bebidas japonesas con confianza. Nuestras máquinas expendedoras muestran ingredientes y fechas de vencimiento antes de pagar, aceptan múltiples métodos de pago y te permitirán probar algo nuevo y diferente.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="#how-it-will-work"
        class="bg-plum-soft text-white font-medium px-8 py-3 rounded-component shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-plum-soft/90 transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-4 ring-plum-soft/30"
      >
        Conocer la idea
      </a>
      <a
        href="#products"
        class="bg-white text-plum-soft font-medium px-8 py-3 rounded-component border-2 border-mist-gray hover:border-plum-soft/50 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-4 ring-plum-soft/30"
      >
        Ver productos que tendremos
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 -z-10 w-full h-full opacity-50">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-32 h-32 bg-sakura-light rounded-full filter blur-2xl animate-blob"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-1/4 w-48 h-48 bg-sakura-medium rounded-full filter blur-3xl animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/3 w-24 h-24 bg-plum-soft/50 rounded-full filter blur-2xl animate-blob animation-delay-4000"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes blob {
    0% {
      transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1);
    }
    33% {
      transform: translate(30px, -50px) scale(1.1);
    }
    66% {
      transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.9);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1);
    }
  }

  .animate-blob {
    animation: blob 7s infinite;
  }

  .animation-delay-2000 {
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }

  .animation-delay-4000 {
    animation-delay: 4s;
  }
</style>
